   <topic>table.IS_VALID Function</topic>
    <description>Is the current table valid.</description>
   <syntax>Result_Flag as L = Is_Valid()</syntax>
  
   <discussion><![CDATA[
The <TBL>.IS_VALID() method returns .T. (TRUE) if the table is valid; otherwise, it returns .F. (FALSE).
 ]]>  </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
dim ptr as P
ptr = table.open("customer")
? ptr.is_valid() ? .T.
]]></example>
   
